					- <a href="http://www.silverframework.com/blog" target="_blank"><strong>SilverFramework blog</strong></a> <font size=1>(opens in new window)</font><br />
					- <a href="http://www.silverframework.com" target="_blank"><strong>Purchase a valid license</strong></a> <font size=1>(opens in new window)</font><br />
					<br />
					<p>The SilverFramework for Magento is &copy; 2010 <a href="http://www.silverframework.com">SilverFramework.com</a>.</p>
					</div>
					</div>					
					]]></comment>
						<label>About SilverFramework</label>
						<frontend_type>text</frontend_type>
						<sort_order>1</sort_order>
						<show_in_default>1</show_in_default>
						<show_in_website>1</show_in_website>
						<show_in_store>1</show_in_store>
						

						<fields>
							<serial translate="label">
								<label>Serialnumber</label>
								<frontend_type>text</frontend_type>
								<sort_order>1</sort_order>
								<show_in_default>1</show_in_default>
								<show_in_website>1</show_in_website>
								<show_in_store>1</show_in_store>
								<comment><![CDATA[Note: If you have several domains/store-levels in your Magento installation you must select each Store in the upper left dropdown (Current Configuration Scope) and type in the licensecode for each of them.]]></comment>									
						</serial>
						</fields>
					</general>
				</groups>
			</silverframework_about>			
			
		</sections>
	</config>
